Package courses

Class Summary
Catalogue Contains information for all Schedules in general.
Course Contains information about a course like course title, level, number of credit hours, etc., but not information about a specific section like who teaches it.
DaySlot DaySlot is a combination of days on which a Section may be offered.
Schedule Represents a Schedule.
Section Sections represent actual course offerings.
TestCourse A series of tests.
TestSchedule Contains a series of tests for the Schedule class.
TestSection  
TestTime Tests the methods from Time class.
Time The time of day on a 24 hour clock.
TimeSlot Represents a combination of Days and a duration of time when a Section can meet.
 

Enum Summary
Day Provides the days of the week individually or as a list of all days.
GeneralTime A general division of the day.
